<h2 id="api-层设计prompt-与-message-的协议无关抽象">API 层设计：Prompt 与 Message 的协议无关抽象</h2>
<h3 id="message-体系统一表达对话上下文">Message 体系：统一表达对话上下文</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 核心接口：所有消息类型的基类</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">interface</span> <span class="nc">Message</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">String</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">getContent</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">           </span><span class="c1">// 消息内容</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">MessageType</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">getMessageType</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// 枚举：USER/ASSISTANT/SYSTEM/TOOL</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">Map</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">String</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Object</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">getMetadata</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// 扩展元数据</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 具体实现</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">SystemMessage</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;你是一个专业的Java技术顾问&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">   </span><span class="c1">// 设定角色</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">UserMessage</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;解释一下Spring的AOP原理&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">        </span><span class="c1">// 用户输入</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">AssistantMessage</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;Spring AOP 基于动态代理...&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="c1">// AI回复</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ToolResponseMessage</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;tool_call_id&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s">&#34;{\&#34;temp\&#34;:25}&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">//</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">工具返回</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>设计要点</strong>：<code>MessageType</code> 枚举确保了无论底层模型使用什么字段名（OpenAI 的 <code>role</code>/<code>content</code>，Claude 的 <code>type</code>/<code>text</code>），上层业务代码始终使用统一类型。</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>